message: To get a score of 100, identify items that can be successfully processed into liquids, then combine them. The 'filter' tool works well on all gases (mundane and magical) and magical liquids, turning them into positive-value filtered liquids. The 'vial' tool works well on mundane solids, turning them into positive-value extracted liquids. Avoid using 'vial' on liquids and 'filter' on solids, as these generally result in negative values. To achieve 100 points, combine either a filtered magical item (gas or liquid) with a filtered mundane gas, OR a filtered magical item (gas or liquid) with a vialed mundane solid. Both resulting items in the combination should be positive-value liquids.
